MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: (apps|packages)/.+\.(ts|tsx)$
MATCH_CONTENT: (===\s*['"](SYSTEM|SOCIAL|INTERNAL|CARTRIDGE|ADMIN|FACT|PRESENCE|TICKER|REJECTION)\.|type:\s*['"](SYSTEM|SOCIAL|INTERNAL|CARTRIDGE|ADMIN|FACT|PRESENCE|TICKER|REJECTION)\.|\[\s*['"](SYSTEM|SOCIAL|INTERNAL|CARTRIDGE|ADMIN|FACT|PRESENCE|TICKER|REJECTION)\.)
ADVISORY: |
  Raw event-namespace string literal in non-definition position. Import
  `Events` from `@pecking-order/shared-types` instead — e.g.
  `Events.Social.SEND_MSG`, not `'SOCIAL.SEND_MSG'`.
  Source of truth: packages/shared-types/src/events.ts.
